@node intro "DMC-2-HTML - Introduction"
@{line}
@{b}Introduction@{ub}
@{line}
@{line}
DMC-2-HTML is a utility to convert articles created for Andy Gibson's Disk Magazine Creator (DMC Gold V3.0 only) into HTML.
@{line}
@{line}
Currently DMC-2-HTML supports the following features:
@{line}
@{line}
@{tab}- Converts just a single file or an entire directory (non-recursive)@{line}
@{tab}- Header codes are converted@{line}
@{tab}- Normal font colour codes are converted@{line}
@{tab}- Flashing font colour codes are converted* (excludes multi-cycle flashing)@{line}
@{tab}- Text styles codes are converted@{line}
@{tab}- All unnecessary codes are stripped@{line}
@{line}
*Please note that not all browsers support flashing text.
@{line}
@endnode

